               "name": "Beatriz Dias",
               "history": [
                  "After studying documents that also had part of João Ramalho's testament (<htcite0>), the genealogist Luiz G. Silva Leme changed his initial conclusion, that she was João Ramalho's daughter (<htcite1>; <htcite2>), but there is not any primary source that allows us to reach confirm this relationship.",
